<br>
At 56 with c3 and my cha buff i run at 255 255 int cha at all times.  There are many items that have major cha plusses to them.  The best of which is the dark beguilers robe from Nathyn in Katta.......takes a small raid force of 60 to do him but the robe has stats but the highlight is 100 cha.<br>
<br>
Also look into drakkel wolf claws they drop during the 8th coldain shawl quest and they are nice piercing weapon with 10 int and 10 cha plus more stats to include a proc of wandering mind.  Always fun to tank with the warriors on a mana mob to have more mana than when you started.<br>
